milestones.description: Porterfield and Paul Stirling's 192-run partnership is IRE's highest for the 1st wicket in ODIs, breaking the record of 177 between Porterfield and Paul Stirling
Ireland's 222-run win against U.A.E. is the largest margin of victory in terms of runs in ODIs, beating 133-run win against Canada
This is the lowest match aggregate (404) involving teams U.A.E. & Ireland in ODIs
